        <mxCell id="M1Ehr8ry5uMqj8WjXJBm-19" value="NETWORK FLOW:&#xa;1. User connects to Master Node&#xa;2. Master accesses Internet via Global IP&#xa;3. Master distributes to Workers via Local Network&#xa;4. All nodes communicate through D-Link Switch&#xa;&#xa;KEY FEATURES:&#xa;• Dual-homed Master (Local + Global)&#xa;• Centralized Internet Gateway&#xa;• Switched Local Network Topology" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
